Edit: Ok, so I did some digging and found the actual comment. Guess you can't trust everything on the boards.<br>
<br>
==============<br>
<br>
I was cruising the boards and read some responses to the recent changes to one of the events in Acrylia, thought I'd take a minute and dispel a rumor. I hope the author of this post doesn't mind me using it. <br>
<br>
'Did RoF last night and man did they nerf it! From 4th boss till 5th boss the skele's that pop all do AE complete heal. We had about 40 peeps there and got owned twice. Never even made it to the 5th boss.' <br>
<br>
After the fourth boss the mobs that spawned were Level 2, this was a result of a bug, and fixing it brought the mobs up to the appropriate level. There is a chance that a healer will spawn, but there are none that can cast AE heals. <br>
<br>
I apologize for the bug having slipped past us. <br>
<br>
